OL,4,CDrug firm fined for huge price rise
OL,5,Cthat hit NHS
OL,6, A drug company that increased the price
OL,7, of a crucial thyroid remedy more than
OL,8, 10-fold has prompted fines of more than
OL,9, #100m by the competition watchdog.
OL,11,FAdvanz pushed up the price of thyroid
OL,12,Ftablet packs from #20 in 2009 to #248
OL,13,Fin 2017, making the drug unaffordable
OL,14,Ffor the NHS.
OL,16,FIt "exploited a loophole enabling it to
OL,17,Freap much higher profits", the
OL,18,FCompetition and Markets Authority said.
OL,20,FThe fine applies to Advanz and two
OL,21,Fprivate equity firms.
